    {
      "id": "setup_track_deck",
      "text": "The track deck is prepared by following the steps below be performed:",
      "bullets": [
        {
          "text": "The double-sided overview map Agent Harper will find next to on the scenario overview card."
        },
        {
          "text": "The 6 unique opponents with the Suspect trait and the 6 unilateral locations with the hiding feature are divided into 2 separate Split Stack: A stack should only consist of suspect opponents consist, the other just hiding places."
        },
        {
          "text": "1 card from each pile is determined at random (1 suspect opponent and 1 hiding place) and hidden without looking at it, placed under the overview map to find Agent Harper."
        },
        {
          "text": "The 10 remaining cards of the 2 piles become a deck mixed together, called the track deck. This deck is placed next to the scenario overview map."
        }
      ]
    },
